These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different pets are kept: mouse, hamster, ferret, bird, guinea-pig, horse, turtle
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, adventure, thriller, fantasy, sports, crime, horror
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 4. the person watching horror movies is the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is the owner of the bird##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
11. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
12. the owner of the ferret is the person watching sports movies##1
13. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig      | ferret      | horse    | turtle    | hamster | mouse     | bird     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | sports | thriller | martial-arts | crime   | horror | adventure |

