.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
There 7 different types of food: papaya, grapefruit, lime, onion, broccoli, eggplant, lemon
There are 7 different favourite colors: ivory, grey, lavender, blood-red, green, lilac, aquamarine
 1. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
 2. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
 3. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who likes lilac is the person eating onion##1
 7. the person eating grapefruit is the person who likes green##1
 8. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 9. the person eating onion is the person who likes lilac##1
10. the person eating lime is between the person who likes lilac and the person eating grapefruit##2
11. the person eating eggplant is in the middle##1
12. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Food   | grapefruit   | lime | onion | eggplant   | lemon | papaya | broccoli |
| Color           | green | ivory          | lilac    | grey | blood-red     | lavender      | aquamarine    |

