.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: photography, board-games, magic-tricks, puzzles, reading, collecting, chess
The people use 7 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, boat, airplane, scooter, subway, ship
 1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
 6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is chess##1
12. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Hobby   | puzzles        | board-games  | collecting | magic-tricks | reading           | chess           | photography  |
| Transport    | quad-bike | airplane | ship   | boat    | scooter | subway | train |

