10. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
12. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
13. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3

