 3. the futuristic house is between the farmhouse house and the person who likes grey##2
 4. the cottage house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes white and the person who likes grey##2
 6. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
 7. the person who likes ebony is the modern house##1
 8. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 9. the colonial house is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes white is on the left of the colonial house##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is in an even position##4
12. the cottage house is in an odd position##4
13. the futuristic house is the person who likes chestnut##1
14. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
15. the person who likes ebony is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who likes black is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
