City: hamburg, berlin, liverpool, nizza, paris, london, boston
 1. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
 2. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
 5. the bongani-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the person traveling to hamburg##2
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 8. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 9. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
11. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
12. the person traveling to liverpool is the dannemann-smoker##1
13. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |   3   |   4   |   5    |  6   |    7    |
| Cigar   | baccarat | davidoff | pall-mall  | alhambra | bongani | dannemann  | vegafina   |
| City           | boston  | nizza | london | hamburg   | berlin | liverpool | paris |

