 1. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the british is on the left or right of the french##3
 5. the canadian is in an even position##4
 6. the canadian is on the right of the thai##1
 7. the dutch is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the french is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the british##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the dutch is the person who's birthday is in december##1
12. the australian is the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the australian##3
14. the canadian is in an even position##4
15. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
