 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 9. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is between the montecristo-smoker and the person who's sport is cricket##2
11. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4   |    5    |       6       |      7      |
| Sport   | basketball     | cricket   | sailing      | swimming | surfing    | climbing | parkour |
| Cigar       | old-henry | baccarat | vegafina | montecristo  | alhambra | blend     | prince    |

