 1. the dunhill-smoker is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
 3. the owner of the dog is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is the baccarat-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
 6. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
 7. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the bongani-smoker is the owner of the goat##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
12. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the dog is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
14. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
