.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
City: new-york, paris, london, berlin, prague, marseilles, boston
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, february, august, march, june, october, january
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
 3. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
10. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| City          | marseilles   | london | boston | new-york | prague | paris | berlin |
| Birthday   | june | january      | october     | august  | march | april         | february    |

 